data.description: This amazing home boasts 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths and over 3600sqft of coziness!  There is a dedicated office, game room, media room and more.  Solar panels come installed and ready to save you money in this Texas heat!  Located in the quiet Arcadia subdivision, you have a pool, jogging trails and playground to enjoy as well.  Let's make this home yours!!
